你能够调用以下的API:
[['ArxivSearch.get_arxiv_article_information', {'name': 'ArxivSearch.get_arxiv_article_information', 'description': 'Run Arxiv search and get the article meta information.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'query', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the content of search query'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'content', 'description': 'a list of 3 arxiv search papers, including published date, title, authors, and summary'}]}], ['InvestmentInstitution.get_investment_decisions', {'name': 'InvestmentInstitution.get_investment_decisions', 'description': 'Retrieve investment decisions made by a specific institution over a given period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institution', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the investment institution.'}, {'name': 'period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time period for the decisions, in the format YYYY-MM-DD to YYYY-MM-DD.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'decisions', 'description': 'A list of investment decisions including date, asset, and decision type.'}]}], ['InvestmentInstitution.analyze_decision_data', {'name': 'InvestmentInstitution.analyze_decision_data', 'description': 'Analyze investment decision data for specific biases.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'data', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The data to be analyzed, typically the return data from InvestmentInstitution.get_investment_decisions.'}, {'name': 'bias_type', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of bias to analyze, e.g., confirmation bias.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis_result', 'description': 'The result of the analysis, indicating the presence and extent of the specified bias.'}]}], ['InvestmentInstitution.provide_investment_strategies', {'name': 'InvestmentInstitution.provide_investment_strategies', 'description': 'Provide investment strategies based on the analysis of decision data.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'analysis_result', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The result of the analysis from InvestmentInstitution.analyze_decision_data.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'strategies', 'description': 'A list of investment strategies to mitigate the identified biases.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
